Configure routing middleware in your app and add following end points
1)Add an end point for controller routes with the name "default" and the pattern should be {controller}/{action}/{id?} set the default controller as 
Employees, action method as Index
2)Add another endpoint for only GET requests with the patterns "/hello/{name:alpha}" where it accepts only alphabets [a-zA-Z]
3)Add another endpoint for only GET requests with RequireHost. The host name should be "contoso.com"
